snippet.title: Sonic x Minecraft DLC: Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Celebrate thirty years of Sonic with this fast-paced Minecraft DLC! Dash through this 3D runner filled with iconic locations, familiar foes, and the blockiest rings you’ll ever see. Get it now from Minecraft Marketplace!

AUDIO DESCRIPTION version: https://youtu.be/MIlHguuBwjE
